Interface ConfigHolder

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
BooleanField, ChoiceField, ConfigField, DoubleField, FieldGroup, IntField, IntListField, RoleFields, RoleGroup, StringField, StringListField, TimeField
public interface ConfigHolder

Collection of values for configuring an experiment. The hierarchy can be rendered as HTML to provide a web-based interface. When the experimenter updates the configuration to the server, the values can be read back out of the HTML fields.
